-- Eskom of South Africa May Get World Bank Loan For Renewable Energy Plans
-- B y   R o n   D e r b y
-- 2010-10-14T15:23:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-14/eskom-of-south-africa-may-get-world-bank-loan-for-renewable-energy-plans.html
Eskom Holdings Ltd. said it may be
able to get a $1 billion loan from the World Bank for renewable
energy.  The timing of the loan is still to be set, the
Johannesburg-based company said in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
